🎮 Pathfinding Chase Game – Short & Clean Explanation
🔹 1. HTML (Structure)
Canvas use kiya gaya hai game display ke liye
Score aur High Score show hota hai
Title + scoreboard UI
🎨 2. CSS (Design)
Dark theme background
Canvas border aur shadow for game look
Simple aur clean interface
⚙️ 3. JavaScript (Game Logic)
👤 Player
Arrow keys / WASD se move karta hai
Walls ke through nahi ja sakta
🤖 Enemy (AI)
Player ko chase karta hai
BFS Pathfinding use hoti hai (shortest path find karne ke liye)
Har frame par nahi, sirf kuch frames baad path update hota hai (efficient)
🪙 Coin System
Random position par spawn hota hai
Player coin collect kare to score increase hota hai
📌 4. Collision System
Player vs Coin → Score increase
Player vs Enemy → Game Over
🔄 5. Game Loop
update() → movement & logic
draw() → graphics render
requestAnimationFrame() → smooth animation
💡 6. Special Features
Grid-based movement system
BFS pathfinding (AI intelligence)
Smooth collision physics
High score tracking
